Add following to steam as a Non-Steam Game
    EmulationStation Desktop Edition (ES-DE)  AppImage
    RetroArch(launch script)
    Lutris(launch script)


install games on separate drive(partition)
    create a directory(SteamLibrary) in the partition
    Open Steam -> Settings -> Storage -> Add Drive
    add directory(SteamLibrary)


Steam games are typically in ~/.steam and ~/.local/share/Steam


